1. Connect Ethernet LAN cable to Pi
2. Open Command Prompt 
> Type in 'arp -a' to search for Pi IP Address (Normally 192.168... with type = dynamic)
> If failed, unplug Ethernet cable from Pi and replug after 5 seconds 
> Type in 'ping pi.local' 
> Pinging should be successful now 
3. Open Visual Studio Code
> Download 'Remote-ssh' extension/plug-in
